author: Marcus Cho
title: Lil Yachty Joins the Nautica Team as a Creative Designer
text:
Lil Yachty is no stranger to the clothing industry , and to kick off 2017 he joined up with Nautica to be one of its creative designers.
The announcement came after Lil Yachty served as the face of Nautica’s capsule collection for Urban Outfitters which released last year, and this time around his role will include designing more collections and appearing in upcoming media campaigns.
“Nautica is like a part of me,” said Lil Yachty. “It’s for kids, sailors, grown men and cool people. The designs — the old designs, the new designs, I think it’s dope. There’s not really much out there like Nautica.”
Lil Yachty also recently starred in an Alexander Wang ad campaign .
